{"tid":2137094,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"60歲手足，還押中過生日","createTime":"2020-08-02T15:41:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-02T16:57:44.000Z","uid":211994,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3a271fd3ee63f7eefc6d6d634db543c0e037e42a","tid":2137094,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T15:41:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/sparkalliancehk/10481\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsparkalliancehk%2F10481&d=Surr%2FXenqJySG8qcND35%2F13VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=e0267bbc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sparkalliancehk/10481</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dEuX1Jc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdEuX1Jc.jpg&h=8c109b10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【還押中過生日】<br />\n<br />\n年逾六十、已經退休，本可含飴弄孫及安享晚年的全叔，涉嫌於今年3月向上水已婚警察宿舍投擲汽油彈，原被控縱火的他，前天突然被額外加控管有腐蝕性物品，以及管有物品意圖作非法用途使用兩罪。從來全叔甚麼資源都不欲擁有，香煙、私家飯他都一一推卻，每次都說希望把資源留給其他有需要的年輕人。連保釋候審他也暫不欲申請，從三月開始一直還押至今已近五個月了，正等候本月下旬再度上庭。<br />\n<br />\n面對失去自由的日子，個多星期之後更是全叔自己的生日，而陪伴自己的，就只有冰冷的四面圍牆。<br />\n<br />\n本平台現呼籲同道向全叔送上生日卡或祝福語，希望他縱然面對政權打壓，仍然知道有很多市民正關心他的情況，亦希望他不要氣餒。<br />\n<br />\n同道可將生日卡及信件寄到本平台：尖沙咀郵箱98697號，我們會將大家的心意轉交到全叔手中。<br />\n<br />\n只要每人多做一步，就可為被囚禁的義士送上無限溫暖；一句生日快樂，已可令在囚者感覺不被遺忘。他們身陷港共黑獄的這段漫長苦日子，需要我們每一個人支持他一起撐過去。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sparkalliancehk/photos/a.1989972677956521/2830806490539798/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsparkalliancehk%2Fphotos%2Fa.1989972677956521%2F2830806490539798%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=Surr%2FXenqJySG8qcND35%2F13VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=e10f26ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sparkalliancehk/photos/a.1989972677956521/2830806490539798/?type=3</a>"},{"pid":"fab360db1d9d7daeaef7f60a35160ecf7c8ba33f","tid":2137094,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T15:41:48.000Z","msg":"全叔生日快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"386b545ffb27c79ac6bd2ff37ce0522f86ac7e2e","tid":2137094,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T15:42:43.000Z","msg":"都係開心啲好啲，全叔生日快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12bf26e15922c54b68934188731e32e9428a7a23","tid":2137094,"uid":223208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T15:44:06.000Z","msg":"生日快樂"},{"pid":"f947c046e6a829e7e93ecb79b23801c28a0d30c1","tid":2137094,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T15:44:29.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"531a441e72b192d89fba348232687499e7a35ff1","tid":2137094,"uid":268217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T15:45:12.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5467b5f75fc6c1a73f09c6de6cfa12866359f305","tid":2137094,"uid":125861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T15:46:41.000Z","msg":"手足保重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cb9642795dde1f937ceed838516c9fd3218455f","tid":2137094,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T15:46:58.000Z","msg":"推下先"},{"pid":"7055516468f4ebf242871775e3c8badbaa7578cc","tid":2137094,"uid":102713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T15:47:11.000Z","msg":"生日快樂全叔"},{"pid":"0fb6a65faaeca24c113062e022c8d04b3720475e","tid":2137094,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T15:47:42.000Z","msg":"寫張生日卡俾全叔啦，有哂地址喇<img src=\"/assets/f